Class ClientUI

java.lang.Object
Presentation.UIBasic
Presentation.ClientUI
public class ClientUI
extends UIBasic
class used for the reister and login funtions in this class we have the functions of a client to place order and to filter products by any fields he wants. For each order placed a bill.txt with the clients name is created
